# -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

QUICK_LOOK - Perform extremely basic reduction to give a "quick look"
to raw data.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This recipe copies raw data into the reduced data directory, then
reads headers and creates a night log file. No further data processing
is done.

=head1 NOTES

=over 4

This recipe is suitable for all spectroscopy instruments.

=back

=head1 OUTPUT DATA

=over 4

A copy of the raw data in $ORAC_DATA_OUT, with suffix _mraw.

=back

=head1 RELATED RECIPES

REDUCE_SINGLE_FRAME.

